# [PROJECT_NAME] Refactor Playbook

## Refactor Triggers
- Any source file > 500 lines (hard trigger).
- New file exceeds 400 lines (soft target exceeded).
- Repeated logic appears in multiple modules.
- Route/controller files mixing business logic and persistence logic.

## Refactor Workflow
1. Identify bounded module and expected interface.
2. Add/adjust targeted test first when behavior is at risk.
3. Extract module with clear dependency direction.
4. Keep public API stable unless change is intentional and documented.
5. Re-run smoke + targeted tests + verify gate.
6. Update docs, repository map, and changelog in same change.

## Release Gate
- No unresolved failing tests.
- Verify command passes.
- Updated docs reflect final structure and commands.
